These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, designer, accountant, analyst
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, thai, argentine, italian
1. the designer is between the scientist and the thai##2
2. the designer is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
3. the designer is somewhere between the analyst and the scientist##7
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the analyst is on the right of the argentine##1
6. the thai is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Job   | accountant | analyst       | designer | scientist        |
| Nationality      | argentine  | thai | italian        | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, ebony, lavender, blue
House: palace, cottage, craftsman, victorian
1. the victorian house is somewhere between the craftsman house and the person who likes lavender##7
2. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
3. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
5. the victorian house is between the craftsman house and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Color     | lavender | ebony       | blue         | green     |
| House   | cottage   | victorian | craftsman | palace |

