.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, mexican, french
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, alhambra, old-henry, bluemaster
1. the nigerian is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##7
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the french##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the bluemaster-smoker and the colombian##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | french | mexican | nigerian  |
| Cigar   | old-henry | pall-mall  | bluemaster   | alhambra |

