.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, red, azure, white
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, adventure, animation
1. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the person who likes white##7
3. the person who likes azure is the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who likes red is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Color   | red | apricot | white       | azure |
| Movie-Genre   | musical      | crime   | adventure | animation  |

