.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, blueberry, cherry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, aconite, dahlia
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
2. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating pumpkin##7
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
6. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5
7. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food         | blueberry | pumpkin   | cherry | spinach |
| Flower   | tulip      | sunflower | dahlia      | aconite |

