.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
House: townhouse, ranch-style, palace, farmhouse
City: hamburg, miami, berlin, london
1. the palace house is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left of the palace house##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
6. the person traveling to london is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to miami##7
7. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| House      | ranch-style | townhouse      | palace | farmhouse     |
| City   | hamburg    | london | miami   | berlin |

