2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the art-deco house##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
4. the tower house is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to hamburg##7
5. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
6. the tower house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| City          | san-francisco    | berlin   | nizza | hamburg  |
| House   | cape-cod | cottage | tower    | art-deco |

