.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, coffee
House: modern, victorian, cottage, gothic-revival
1. the person drinking fanta is not the gothic-revival house##6
2. the cottage house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
3. the person drinking coffee is the cottage house##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking cola##7
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the cottage house##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee | hot-chocolate | fanta | cola |
| House           | cottage   | gothic-revival    | modern       | victorian  |

