.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, july, february
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, puzzles, chess, photography
1. the person who's birthday is in november is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's birthday is in october##7
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Birthday           | february | november | july | october |
| Hobby   | photography         | chess      | woodworking | puzzles            |

