4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking coffee and the havana-smoker##2
6. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere between the havana-smoker and the person drinking coffee##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
