2. the palace house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person playing canasta is not the futuristic house##6
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
6. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the futuristic house and the art-deco house##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
