.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, ice-hockey, soccer, skiing
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, whist, bridge
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is not the person playing backgammon##6
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person who's sport is soccer##7
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Sport       | skiing | surfing | ice-hockey | soccer |
| Game   | canasta   | bridge      | backgammon        | whist  |

