2. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who likes chestnut##7
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
4. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday      | september   | october | july | april   |
| Color   | amber | chestnut   | lavender | orange |

