4. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the person traveling to boston##7
5. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the owner of the rabbit##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Pet           | rabbit | turtle | hamster | bird  |
| City   | boston     | colone   | venice    | london |

