.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, chinese, colombian, indian
There 4 different types of food: kale, apple, lime, corn
1. the colombian is somewhere between the person eating kale and the chinese##7
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating apple##1
3. the indian is on the left of the polish##1
4. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Nationality         | chinese    | colombian | indian     | polish |
| Food   | lime | corn  | apple | kale |

 